AM I?

MY FACE MIGHTLOOK MEAN, BUTIM FRIENDLY :)
WHO AM I?

I am a proud Brazilian who lives in Canada who is a creative Developer & Designer. You might know my work, but I would like to share a bit more about who the man behind the work is.

1

Release

A person who loves nature, music, exercise, sports, and general well-being. I do my best to live the most balanced life possible. Life is a gift that we must not take for granted. Nothing is more important to me than the peace of mind of my loved ones and being in the best mental and physical shape possible.

The fact that the word 'work' is a part of my alias is ironic because it is not my number one priority. It is on the same level of importance as all other areas of my life.

MAIN PILLARS

Details

It is my understanding that in order to be a successful person, I must balance and work on all pillars of my life equally. Here are some of the main pillars that I work on daily.

  • Health

    My physical and emotional health are my top priorities. I exercise every day and I listen to (and even sing) my favorite music. And I think that I sound pretty good :)

  • Family

    My family and my loved ones are very important to me. I know that I wouldn't be who I am today without their love, care and support.

  • Faith

    My faith is my foundation. It helps to keep me grounded. It also helps me to be successful and achieve my goals. My daily prayer enables me to connect and have a deeper relationship with God.

  • Intellectual

    I invest time in reading, learning and staying up-to-date with what is going on in the world.

  • Professional

    I continuously improve my skills and I am always seeking new ways to help my clients achieve their goals.
